snippet.textDisplay: All the parts sounded great, if taken individually. But somehow when transitioning from one vocal section to the next, it didn't feel natural or smooth. In some places it sounded like that vocal section did not belong there. It didn't feel "Coke Studio" enough. Good enough for an upcoming band's first performance, but not what we've come to expect from Coke Studio. You know I've heard many of these artists before, and I know they can be brought together more cohesively than this. This lacks that pinch of panache that we've come to expect from Coke Studio.
